entries.femaleVariant: We cannot pass that way.
Hellman's prolly inside the AV, being held.
Easy. We can help each other.
Let him go. You're done.
Easy, now. Not too late for everyone to walk outta this alive.
Look around! You're fresh outta choices.
You don't know, or you don't wanna say?
I just want Hellman.
You don't have a choice.
Listen. This isn't about you.
You don't know, or you don't wanna tell us?
You all right?
Thanks for savin' my ass, V.
We'll go around, take them from the other side.
Sorry about your people, but I need to keep movin'.
I'm losing my patience.
We'll see about that.
I-I don't know where they took him!
Look, you. You got two seconds to make up your damn mind. Aldecaldos will ride up here any minute now.
Scorpion, the rest... I'm sorry we didn't get here sooner.
They were good people. Great people. They didn't have to die here.
I gotta get Hellman. Will you help?
I'm going after them. You stay with Mitch.
Panam, listen. I know it's not the best time, but I need Hellman. You promised to help – that still hold?
I'll go after 'em.
I want the man this AV was carrying.
I should have stopped him.
I tried. He wouldn't have listened to you, either. Never was much of a listener.
If not for those damned glitches, I could have warned them... This is all my doing...
Mitch and Scorpion are alive. We'll find them.
Now!
...if you leave, now, and wait for our call!
Probably keepin' Hellman in the AV.
Mind that launcher. It will blow us to bits if we approach.
Time to clean up around here, you bastards!
Path's clear.
Step back!
That's all of 'em.
A great pity.
Back, toss your weapons! Or I'll shoot!
Panam. Shoot 'im.
I repeat – drop your weapons! NOW!
I need the guy who was ridin' this AV. You know anything? See anything?
That pilot didn't have to die. He was this close to caving.
He was armed, close to panic. Coulda done something stupid. Like kill me.
Save your breath, V.
Took him with 'em. In our cars.
West. Small unit, your passenger's entourage.
Wait.
I am going with you. I promised I would help.
Besides. Those bastards killed Scorpion. I won't let that go.
Don't argue with 'er, V. No point.
I'll help you settle the score with Kang Tao.
Revenge? That's why you're still helping me?
Scorpion and the rest... Look, I know how you feel. I mean it.
Wonder why you're stayin on board. Is it just about revenge?
Does it matter? I want to catch the bastards that killed my friend. But I also shook hands with you.
The bikes are fine.
Are you all right?
Just some scratches.
You fucking morons!
For fuck's sake, fucking shoot him already!
Shut the fuck up!
Fuck!
Hop on.
Why in the hell were they following the AV?! The fools!
Listen. We saw Mitch. They probably got Scorpion, too. We'll find them, help them out.
entries.maleVariant: Listen. We saw Mitch. They prolly got Scorpion, too. We'll find them, help 'em out.

entries.femaleVariant: I'll handle the launcher, you cover me from here.
Stay in the car. You're hurt. Won't be too much help out there anyway.
You're already blown to bits.
OK, here's the plan – you stay in the car, I...
Panam, hate to break it to ya, but you're hurt.
Listen. I get that launcher outta our way, I'll let you know. Then you go in and help me with the rest. Deal?
entries.maleVariant: Listen. I get that launcher outta the way, I'll let you know. Then you go in and help me with the rest. Deal?

entries.femaleVariant: Don't be an idiot. This is just a scratch. Let's take out the launcher, I will try to...
No. You stay in the car. Sorry, but you're just gonna slow me down.
Yes, ma'am.
If they're still alive…
They're alive. Everything's gonna be OK.
We called for backup!
Bullshit.
Last chance. You don't gotta die today. Let's talk.
Why should I believe you?!
Let him go and tell me where your passenger is.
Hell no. He's lying.
Let me get the comms back up, I'll buzz the unit, we'll talk, but only if...
Panam!
I'm sorry about Scorpion.
Didn't have to kill the pilot.
Stubborn bastard.
I could not risk the life of a friend. The one I still have left.
He was terrified. All he wanted to hear was he had a chance to get outta this alive.
I wonder what you would have done in my shoes.
Everything OK? You need anything?
Where?
Must be lookin' for a way to call base.
So you're the ones who hit 'em with that EMP?
If they took your cars, we might be able to follow their tracks.
Stay with Mitch. I'll be fine.
I always keep my word.
But Panam...
Kang Tao lost contact with their AV. Probably lookin' for it. Better hurry.
What?
You're comin' back for her, right?
I will find those sons of bitches. I swear.
Go. I'll call the crew, get all this cleaned up.
I promise.
You don't see the shit you're in?!
You shoot him, and a millisec later you'll eat lead, too!
I let 'im go, I'll still eat lead!
You know what, V? You're all right. You helped me with Nash, you helped me with Mitch. To my mind, I owe you a favor.
Ah, so that's what this is? Just paying your debts?
No. Nomads always help their own.
By the way, after the whole Nash thing, I didn't think...
V. Listen. I have not forgotten. I will not forget. And I still believed you behaved like a complete asshole.
BUT Mitch is alive thanks to you. And I will not forget that, either. Ever.
Besides, I promised you we would get your Hellman. And we will.
Oooh, so I'm one of yours now? Sounds good.
But you know I--
Hah, true. Thanks.
No, not so fast. I will go with you. Those are my people...
Fucking hell, V! Those are my people out there!
Wait in the car. I'll try and take out the launcher.
I... Fine. But I have Mitch's rifle. I will try to cover you from here.
Good idea. Let's move.
I would have given him a chance. Could've been useful alive.
You're too quick to pull the trigger.
You're right. I would've done the same.
Let's drop it.
The guy coulda been useful. I would've given him a chance.
Useful for what? To call backup? Or to shoot Mitch?
They killed Scorpion, you understand? They killed my friend.
Lecture me all you like. It changes nothing.
Scorpion, Mitch... For anyone I care about, I would have done the same.
V, these guys're soldiers, no strangers to risk. He had a gun against my head. He knew the consequences.
You should think some more about why you wouldn't.
I understand, Panam. I do. But I still think we coulda played this better.
I just think you're a little too trigger-happy, Panam. Should think before you shoot.
Sure...
First Nash, now the pilot...
First you wanted to kill Nash, now the pilot...
No! I don't believe it! You want to drop that bastard's name? Really?!
V – they killed Scorpion! My best friend! What part of that do you not understand?!
I understand that part, Panam. I do. But the pilot still didn't have to die. Woulda been useful alive.
Useful?! For what?! Do you honestly believe he would have taken you to Hellman? That you would have traded hostages?
Don't be so naive, V. They are soldiers, all of them. They follow procedure, no exceptions.
He was just biding his time, waiting for the moment to shoot Mitch, then you and me!
Wake up, V.
Eh, you're right. Woulda done the same.
He'd still be more useful alive than dead.
Come on. Do you really think he would have taken you to Hellman? That you would have exchanged hostages?
People who fly those AVs are the best of the best. Trained right and paid better. That pilot never woulda gone against procedure. Wouldn'ta had the balls.
Do you really believe he broke? He was just looking for a chance to pull that trigger on us.
No point arguing. Still got things to do.
Agreed.
Yeah... We tried to warn you, but... we couldn't connect.
entries.maleVariant: Yeah... We tried to warn you, but... couldn't connect.

entries.femaleVariant: Did you get hit?... Hang on, girl, I'll patch you up.
It's nothing. Let's go.
We couldn't retreat, Panam... They regrouped so fast, started shootin' rockets 'n' shit. I lost everyone.
Everyone? ...Scorpion? Is he here?
Mitch? Mitch!? He's-- He's safe, right?
Panam, I'm sorry. I didn't make it in time...
No. No! Are you sure? No, he...
I still have Mitch's rifle. I will try to cover you from here.
Go.
I'm coming for you.
I... They headed west, for the gas station. But I can't guarantee they're still there!
Panam, you remember the cowboy, don't you?
Shut up!
Panam, you remember the cowboy, don't you?
Shut up!
I need the man who was ridin' this AV. Pilot said they headed west.
Yep, took him with 'em. In our cars. Pilot was tellin' the truth. There's an old gas station out there.
Must be looking for a way to call base.
So you're the ones who hit 'em with that EMP?
Yeah... We tried to warn you, but we couldn't connect.
entries.maleVariant: Yeah... We tried to warn you, but... couldn't connect.

entries.femaleVariant: What's the plan now, V?
Mitch...
Go. I'll call my people. We'll take care of things here.
Let's get to work.
I'll help you settle your score with Kang Tao.
Let's ride. Hope they didn't go far.
We'll see.
Besides – without me, you don't stand a chance.
Your Hellman – I will find him.
Let's delta to that station. Hope you know a shortcut.
If they made it to the station, they're probably waiting on backup. Better hurry.
Mhm. Get ready.
I will destroy them. Every last one of them. Is that a problem for you?
No, and you know it. We're in this together. To the bitter end.
I will destroy them, V. Every last one.
We're in this together. To the bitter end.
We will destroy them. All of them.
Provided you don't hold a grudge about it later.
I won't. And you know it.
We will destroy them. All of them.
We'll leave my ride here, just in case. Just watch the gun, it likes to jam.
Sounds good.
We'll go by bike.
We'll leave my ride here, just in case. Just watch the gun, it likes to jam.
We'll go by bike.
Sounds solid.
The tire tracks start there.
We'll follow them.
Open the door. I'll cover you.
I'm guessin', since you were out here,  you were out here for the AV. The question is why.
Why rush at the AV like that?
Why dive straight for the AV? Didn't notice the markings?
We saw it was damaged, we know this land, we knew where it would fall. We had no idea it was Kang Tao.
I figured they might need help. In the worst case, there'd be good salvage to be had.
Couldn't've been more wrong...
Let's get going. Before they send a rescue party.
V? It's time we moved..
[Stand]
[Sit]
[Open hatch]
[Get out] Preem idea. Let's do this,
It'll all work out, Panam… everything.
Mhm.
I should have seen that Scorpion would want-- Argh…
You did what you could. There's no fault of yours here.
V, what's the hold-up?!
Open the hatch!
[Deactivate turret]
